{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"36490-i-love-my-mom","title":"I Love My Mom","description":"The girl in this story learns from her mother every day. Now she knows many things. Which of these can YOU do?","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Stephanie  Wei"],"illustrators":["Nivong  Sengsakoun"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Room to Read","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/36490-i-love-my-mom"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93898/size3/5514f498477b51945a0f2ac63b7fae8b.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93898/size6/5514f498477b51945a0f2ac63b7fae8b.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69400/size6/46d57f61b2d9cbab1ae615db040d0bb3.jpg","text":"My mom’s name is Lee. She works hard all the time. \nAnd I learn so much from her!","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69401/size6/6eac8d5d1ddeac97b241b13924f97037.jpg","text":"When my mom cooks, I learn to cook too.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69402/size6/4c1fceeadd28b204993472dfa46aa7f6.jpg","text":"When she waters the flowers, \nI learn to water the flowers too.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69403/size6/f1882d3ba00b9584ede191c9be1d0608.jpg","text":"When she washes our clothes, I learn to wash our clothes too.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69404/size6/29c5407580973690fec58c80d8ad13b8.jpg","text":"When she dries our clothes, I learn to dry our clothes too.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69405/size6/4a73eefdb98d534880957c6cb8cf9fce.jpg","text":"My mom also bought me a bicycle and she taught me how to ride it.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69406/size6/a4567772c0c1403ed7474588f55ece1a.jpg","text":"As I ride my bicycle, my mom smiles when I go “WHEEEEEEE!”","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69407/size6/65ac434ae0f3751cbbe66298f9a2bc96.jpg","text":"At night, my mom makes the bed. I learn how to make the bed too.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69408/size6/af86ccccf2d6e358494a2cf398a19e35.jpg","text":"Before bedtime, my mom tells me stories.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69409/size6/fe4b11724dc9a0828fee819b2838bdab.jpg","text":"When I'm sleepy, my mom sings me a lullaby.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69410/size6/6fb23768d88c9d4f31325a5b0f532f5d.jpg","text":"I love my mom so much!","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":127}}